# Gallery Directory

Place event photos here.

**Requirements:**
- Size: 1920x1080px or larger (16:9 aspect ratio preferred)
- Format: JPG
- Naming: Use descriptive names (e.g., `2025-opening-ceremony.jpg`)
- File size: Optimize to under 500KB per image

**Example structure:**
```
placeholder-1.jpg
placeholder-2.jpg
2025-opening-ceremony.jpg
2025-speaker-talk.jpg
```
